text: Maccagno con Pino e Veddasca is a comune in the Province of Varese in the Lombardy region in Italy. It was created in 2014 from the former municipalities of Maccagno, Pino sulla Sponda del Lago Maggiore and Veddasca. Category:2014 establishments in Italy Category:Settlements in Varese
title: Maccagno con Pino e Veddasca
